# Memex runtime state.
# Holds engine-managed sidecars: spaced-repetition card scheduling (T11),
# search caches, and any other personal runtime state. Excluded by default
# because review history etc. is noisy in commit history and rarely useful
# to teammates; keeping it local also keeps each user's review queue private.
.state/

# Legacy SR-state path (pre-`.state/` migration) — kept ignored for older
# workspaces that haven't been opened in the new shell yet.
.sr-state.json

# Cached search index (Tantivy). Always regenerable from the markdown corpus.
.search/

# OS / editor noise.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
